{"tid":111919,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"持槍搶三星工廠　350部都係「note7」...搶匪過年自首","createTime":"2017-02-07T17:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T19:02:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29c8ad647d7645feacd4f6cf53de79a8212113eb","tid":111919,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T17:34:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">2017年02月7日 12:32</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2066/d2066097.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2066%2Fd2066097.jpg&h=9797c44c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲台灣也曾有人持槍搶劫Note7。<br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n武漢32歲張姓男子1月30日凌晨和同夥闖入廣東的「三星公司」工廠內，持槍搶走350支三星電話，並逃回老家過年。2月4日，張男在家人的勸說下，自行向警方投案，警方統計後表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">被搶的350支電話共價值50多萬元人民幣（約227萬元新台幣）。</span><br />\n根據《武漢晚報》報導，張男的同夥共有9名，在凌晨闖入廣東省惠州市陳江鎮三星公司工廠內，<span style=\"color: red;\">以持槍並捆綁廠區工作人員的方式，搶走倉庫內350支三星note7。</span><br />\n做案以後，張男馬上逃回自己在武漢的老家。警方得知消息以後，也透過張男的家人展開勸說投案的計畫，並派人在他家附近埋伏，防止他二次潛逃。在親情攻勢下，<span style=\"color: red;\">張男最後在過年後自行投案，向警方說出自己拿搶搶劫350支電話的經過。</span><br />\n警方所統計的電話價值也被微博上的網友注意到，引起激烈討論，「價值50萬元人民幣？等於<span style=\"color: red;\">1支只剩下1400多元人民幣（約6300元新台幣），我買的那時候一支可是賣到快6000元（約2.7萬元新台幣）勒！」</span>、「一支還有1400元的價值？免費我都不敢要！」、「我猜他們一開始不是想偷note7，是不小心偷錯，後來發現難以脫手，乾脆自首了。」、「走私軍火可是重罪，這傢伙也太大膽了！」、「難怪警察要用勸降的，怕他們把手機全炸了吧？」<br />\n▼note7開賣時買氣相當火熱，但後來爆炸事件頻傳，名聲跌落谷底，三星最後也承認錯誤，宣布停產。（圖／業者提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1973/d1973789.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1973%2Fd1973789.jpg&h=0caa9c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170207/861947.htm#ixzz4Y1QRrZGG \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170207%2F861947.htm%23ixzz4Y1QRrZGG%20&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6lzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=c291171c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170207/861947.htm#ixzz4Y1QRrZGG </a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"a14731a9e1e4469886c0e84af3955903c20c49c4","tid":111919,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T17:44:44.000Z","msg":"350個炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e197b15b7ef3b3537c6f67de4bb62fbb69c3a448","tid":111919,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T17:53:01.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3550c284412181f46780d646204acaa1e438caa2","tid":111919,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T18:11:31.000Z","msg":"1月30號？<br />\n大陸仲生產緊軍火？"},{"pid":"dea02f10f44f365d520ad190ab9812ccfe743d66","tid":111919,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T19:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67cbecfcbd0543b4f1d974c3f438a2bd2fe85ad","tid":111919,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗咬狗"},{"pid":"47e8616be6a398086a808e365a65aa0b3f2589b5","tid":111919,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://bestanimations.com/Military/Explosions/nuclear-atom-bomg-explosion-animated-gif-6.gif\" data-thumbnail